text: Write down the output of the given program and show them in dry run table: DECLARE SUB SERIES ( ) CLS CALL SERIES END SUB SERIES ( ) X = 1 Y = 1 FOR P = 1 TO 10 PRINT X; X = X + Y Y = Y + 1 NEXT P END SUB
norm: write down the output of the given program and show them in dry run table: declare sub series ( ) cls call series end sub series ( ) x = 1 y = 1 for p = 1 to 10 print x; x = x + y y = y + 1 next p end sub
